# Suppose you want to deposit a certain amount of money into a savings account with a fixed annual interest rate.
#What amount do you need to deposit in order to have $5,000 in the account after three years?

fa = eval(input("Enter final account value: "))
ai = eval(input("Enter annual interest rate in percent:: "))
mi = ai/12
ny = eval(input("Enter number of years: "))
nm = ny*12
in_de = fa/(1+mi)*nm
print(in_de)
